## ⚙️ **.gitignore**

Save this as `.gitignore` (no file extension) in your project root:

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.log

# Flask cache
instance/
*.db

# Environment
.env
venv/
env/
.venv/

# IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Temporary folders
temp/
__temp__/
*.bak
*.swp

# Large media files (optional, if using Git LFS)
*.mp4
*.avi
*.mov

# Jupyter notebooks (if any)
*.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Backup
*.zip
*.tar
*.gz
